    "description": "建造、制作、耕种、开采、狩猎……拥抱独特信仰，让贵族团结一致。分配丰足财富，满足其雄心壮志。守卫王土，抵御威胁；发展关系，睦邻友邦。与来访者沟通，找出契合之处，扩大你的队伍。开展往来交易，取得神奇物品，强化自身技能。搜刮死人，囚禁或抢劫活人。恐吓囚犯，逼迫其接受奴役生活。你，是想沉浸在英明统治带来崇拜和赞赏中，还是想直面身为暴君的因果报应？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/aaeae8282cb2ffd6ba504bc685a2fc46.poster.avif?t=1770157443\" width=614 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/aaeae8282cb2ffd6ba504bc685a2fc46.webm?t=1770157443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/aaeae8282cb2ffd6ba504bc685a2fc46.mp4?t=1770157443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/be8f629eb8702350f0be9737d996d87c.avif?t=1770157443\" width=615 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/c650fdda43cf881006512b25f78056fe.poster.avif?t=1770157443\" width=614 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/c650fdda43cf881006512b25f78056fe.webm?t=1770157443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/c650fdda43cf881006512b25f78056fe.mp4?t=1770157443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在遥远的大地上，各路凡胎争夺着物质世界的掌控权。众神统治着这个位面，并与其认定的有价值之人分享神力，以此维持平衡。其他位面的栖居者不遗余力地想要染指此处——他们别无他求，一心只想带来混乱。你是一名亢图腊，是能够影响和控制凡胎的半神。尽管还是个新手，但你想要打造一个能够赢得长久认可的王国。<br><br>不过你的运气，到现在为止都很一般……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/8225a834d0b23e0ee742a013b0eaadf8.avif?t=1770157443\" width=615 height=64 /></span><br>凡胎的独特之处，从其身上的<strong>倾向</strong>与<strong>观点</strong>中折射而出。凡胎会有<strong>记忆</strong>，其中记录了对其影响最大的一些互动。凡胎的倾向、观点以及记忆推动着其做出反应和决定。<br><br><i>接纳让凡胎团结一致、欣欣向荣的独特信仰！</i><br><br>斗志昂扬的凡胎会想尽一切办法攀登巅峰，并且以师出有名之姿，让一切敌人闻风丧胆。每次游玩都会围绕一段虚拟的凡胎与互动历史展开，这些是展开故事的基础所在。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/5dda8310d79419576bd4e4b3edd6522c.poster.avif?t=1770157443\" width=614 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/5dda8310d79419576bd4e4b3edd6522c.webm?t=1770157443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/5dda8310d79419576bd4e4b3edd6522c.mp4?t=1770157443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>凡胎会去学习，会互相影响，其技能和雄心也会随之增长。神则会赐予强大能力来嘉奖凡胎的成长。最终，凡胎会衰老、退化，直至死亡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/ef66bf93ad067bc2b9bab36c6b89bff5.avif?t=1770157443\" width=615 height=64 /></span><br>从旁观者的视角控制君主，欣赏王国的美妙风采！漫步树林，享受宁静的美好时光。拿出你从不离身的魔法弓，狩猎鹿群，获取食物。巧舌如簧地讨好商人，压低价格，让你拿下绝佳交易。说服来访贵族，使其变节脱离自己的领主并将全部物品捐赠给你，支持你的事业。亲身体验宏大时刻：从城垛上一跃而下，伏击敌人；施展技能吸引巨兽，同时让你的子民将其击倒。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/d407d5125284f00f2369bcbc1fd6e4b7.poster.avif?t=1770157443\" width=614 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/d407d5125284f00f2369bcbc1fd6e4b7.webm?t=1770157443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/d407d5125284f00f2369bcbc1fd6e4b7.mp4?t=1770157443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/406b16c1c64812f95e683be0cbe2dd89.avif?t=1770157443\" width=615 height=64 /></span><br>但是，在<strong>其他</strong>凡胎之外，这片大地还面临着一场日益严峻的威胁——魔痈现世。打开魔痈，迎接来自恶魔裂隙的挑战。无穷无尽的恶魔之潮会带来逐步提升的奖励。直面异界怪，那甚至能摧毁最坚固防御的恶魔。施展当世法师的力量，在世界毁灭之前击退威胁，封印裂隙。你，是想沉浸在胜利的荣耀中，还是放弃奖赏，选择一条更加安全的道路？这一切都取决于你。<br><br>王国将会延续，只需要有一颗活着的头颅来佩戴王冠。君主的陨落，可能会使长期恩怨背后的郁结烟消云散，也可能会让被遗忘的不公正重现世间。对于新君主的观点将会有所不同，你的子民也会相应地做出反应。<br><br>让子民快乐地活下去，让王国神韵世代传承！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/ec25211f2dd269eef33e116d5577a58f.poster.avif?t=1770157443\" width=614 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/ec25211f2dd269eef33e116d5577a58f.webm?t=1770157443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/ec25211f2dd269eef33e116d5577a58f.mp4?t=1770157443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在这本世界之巨著中，一个王国的覆灭，只不过是某个章节的结束罢了……<br><br>羽化飞升，在这相同的世界中永不停歇地前行！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769420/extras/f8e5ada155475d92e7a998c668d4f30a.avif?t=1770157443\" width=615 height=64 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>让人眼花缭乱的信仰选项带来了极高的可复玩性<br></li><li>诸多解锁项目与值得深入发掘的游戏体验<br></li><li>从天空中下达指令或以第三人称视角控制君主<br></li><li>全面的上手体验<br></li><li>可重复游玩的终局挑战<br></li><li>羽化飞升并在相同的世界中再次出发<br></li><li>通过Steam创意工坊实现了深度模组支持<br></li><li>多项重大更新为你的故事带来全新转折！</li></ul>",
